{"tid":629859,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(温故知新) 聯匯制度下的香港樓市","createTime":"2018-04-15T05:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T16:02:48.000Z","uid":36138,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b7680a41e4bc5a7967e6fdf1ca944f2da62aa8e5","tid":629859,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T05:26:23.000Z","msg":"轉貼原文討論於9年前即2009年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家一定要清楚明白樓市升跌既根本同聯匯有好大好大既關係。樓市後市係點? 大家應該預測得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=10254495&amp;extra=&amp;authorid=3728681&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.discuss.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Faction%3Dthread%26tid%3D10254495%26extra%3D%26authorid%3D3728681%26page%3D1&d=wjLnzjBMS3ebGeoGKzojcDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=b23bb97b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=10254495&amp;extra=&amp;authorid=3728681&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「97年亞洲金融風暴發生後, 港元本應隨經濟下滑而貶值, 但因聯匯的因素, 幣值不可貶, 於是唯有資產貶值, 樓價最多跌了7成.&nbsp;<br />\n08年美國金融海嘯發生後, 港元本應隨經濟的相對稳定而升值, 但因聯匯因素, 幣值不可升, 於是唯有資產升值. 這次升浪會升多少, 暫時無人計得出來, 但我相信, 隨著美元中長期向下的走勢, 這一輪樓價的升幅, 會升到你唔信!&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n07年9月, 當美國因金融風暴出現後, 開始減息之時, 我便力主此講法. 金融海嘯後香港樓價調整再上, 我更堅定了自己的睇法. 事實上, 香港樓市走勢正按我預想的推論運行.&nbsp;」"},{"pid":"e54f110ebd1ae18466c0210ae662687040d53bb0","tid":629859,"uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"this time is different"},{"pid":"563d1e82c58d42eafc5bce96ab6b3dfd7422d171","tid":629859,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T05:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921f0d94a50a25b47322b6e8b15139f4df2c7cf0","tid":629859,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T05:42:45.000Z","msg":"究竟美元多次加息後，而家既美元叫強定叫弱?"